 I started\u00a0to beat\u00a0it. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to me, \u201cYou must be gentle. Verily, gentleness is not in anything but that it beautifies it, and it is not removed from anything but that it\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":913,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/08\/harshness-disgraceful\/","url_meta":{"origin":42657,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Rifq: Cruelty is disgraceful, Allah loves gentleness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Harshness is not found in anything but that it disgraces it. Verily, Allah is kind and He loves kindness.\" Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 466 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24811,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/11\/allah-supports-gentle-people\/","url_meta":{"origin":42657,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Kindness: Allah supports kind and gentle people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ma\u2019dan ibn Abi Talhah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty is kind. He loves kindness and is pleased by it. He offers support for it, that which is not offered for harshness.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 20\/365 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12108,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/06\/gheerah-fahishah-haram-hamd\/","url_meta":{"origin":42657,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Gheerah: Allah prohibits obscenity, loves to be praised","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo one has a greater sense of honor than Allah, so He has made obscenities unlawful in public and in private. And no one loves to be praised more than Allah.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4637, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17151,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/12\/haya-jannah-badha-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":42657,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Modesty in Paradise, shamelessness in Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 12, 2013","format":false,"exc